hits.definition:
企

[qǐ] stand on tiptoe, hope for, look forward to;

    企业 qǐyè enterprise;

    企图 qǐtú attempt;

    企鹅 penguin

斗

[dǒu] 10 liters;

    烟斗 yāndǒu tobacco/opium pipe;

    北斗星 Běidǒuxīng The Big Dipper, The Plow

[dòu] (F 鬥) fight

右

[yòu] right;

    右边 yòubiān right side;

    左右 zuǒyòu around, nearby, more or less

{Compare with 石 shí stone}
